---
import '../styles/tokens.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy | eixo.design</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy policy for eixo.design — how we handle your data." />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/eixo-favicon.png" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header>
      <a href="/">
        <img src="/assets/images/eixo-logo-white.png" alt="eixo.design" />
      </a>
      <a href="/">Back to site</a>
    </header>

    <main>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="meta">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <h2>Controller</h2>
      <p>eixo.design is operated by Natalia Arsand, based in Amsterdam, the Netherlands. For any privacy-related requests, contact <a href="mailto:hello@eixo.design">hello@eixo.design</a>.</p>

      <h2>What we collect and why</h2>
      <p><strong>Contact form</strong> — name, email, company (optional), and message. Used solely to respond to your inquiry. Data is delivered to our email via Cloudflare and not stored in any database.</p>
      <p><strong>Analytics</strong> — with your consent, Google Analytics collects anonymised usage data (pages visited, time on site). No personally identifiable information is collected. You can withdraw consent at any time.</p>

      <h2>Third-party processors</h2>
      <p>Cloudflare (hosting and email delivery), Google Analytics (consent-based analytics), Google Fonts (typography).</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>Analytics cookies are loaded only after your explicit consent. No advertising or tracking cookies are used.</p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>Contact form data is retained in our email as long as necessary. You can request deletion at any time.</p>

      <h2>Your rights (GDPR / AVG)</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access, rectify, erase, restrict processing, or port your personal data. Contact <a href="mailto:hello@eixo.design">hello@eixo.design</a> to exercise these rights.</p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>Updates to this policy will be reflected on this page with an updated date.</p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--white-a8);
  }

  header img {
    height: 20px;
    width: auto;
  }

  header a {
    color: var(--color-subtle);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  header a:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  main {
    max-width: var(--content-text);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-3);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-1);
  }

  .meta {
    color: var(--color-subtle);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-6);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: var(--space-5) 0 var(--space-1);
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-subtle);
    margin: var(--space-3) 0 var(--space-1);
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2);
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
